snippet.title: Net.Attack() | Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3047370/NetAttack/

Unleash your inner hacker skills and code your way to victory in a game where complex algorithms meet intuitive gameplay. Net.Attack() is a dynamic top-down survivor-like roguelite where you create your own abilities with a node-based coding mechanic. Go and dominate the virtual battleboards.
